      "code": "self.self.setIntangibility(true);\nself.effect = self.self.attachEffect(\"global_dust_heavy\", { scaleX: 0.8, scaleY: 0.8 });\nself.effect.scaleX = -self.effect.scaleX;\nreturn;",
