      "code": "self.self.playVoiceSound(1);\nself.self.destroyTimer(self.playDust);\nself.self.createTimer(3, -1, self.playDust);\nself.self.attachEffect(\"global_spark\", { x: self.flipX(20), y: -18 });\nself.frameCount = self.frameCount + self.frameInc * 1.5;\nreturn;",
