    {
      "$id": "26912237-f41d-5fa6-90d7-2868ffdc6528",
      "code": "self.self = /* ? */;\nif ((parent && SSF2API.isReady()) || self.self) {\n\tself.xframe = null;\n\tself.prevYLoc = 0;\n\tself.countDown = 7;\n\tself.self.playSound(\"throw_woosh\");\n}\nreturn;",
